Class SavingsAccountTransactionSummaryWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.fineract.portfolio.savings.domain.SavingsAccountTransactionSummaryWrapper

  • @Component
public final class SavingsAccountTransactionSummaryWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper for dealing with side-effect free functionality related to a SavingsAccount's SavingsAccountTransaction's.
